<p>Notice itâ€™s all commands. Remember, itâ€™s not a real conversation with a computer. No banter, no back and forth. Itâ€™s directions. I am telling a computer what to do and in what order. A computer will only do exactly what it is told. So if we give instructions correctly, things go right. Otherwise, theyâ€™re like wishes to a naive genie: Something is always just a little wrong. Fortunately, you can test your code before having rippling effects across space-time. Not so much with the genie wishes.</p>

<h2 id="lets-recap">Letâ€™s recap:</h2>
